   <head>THE Christian Gouernour.</head>
   <p>
      <hi>From whom</hi>
      <list>
         <item>KINGS on their <hi>Thrones,</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Nobles</hi> in their <hi>Houses,</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Pastors</hi> in their <hi>Charges,</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Magistrates</hi> on <hi>Seats</hi> of <hi>Iustice,</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Priuate men</hi> in their <hi>Families,</hi>
         </item>
      </list>
   </p>
   <p>May draw good Instructions:</p>
   <p>
      <hi>How to</hi>
      <list>
         <item>
            <hi>Rule</hi> their <hi>Subiects.</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Order</hi> their <hi>Seruants.</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Feede</hi> their <hi>Flockes.</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Punish Offendors.</hi>
         </item>
         <item>
            <hi>Gouerne</hi> their <hi>Households</hi>
            <gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>
         </item>
      </list>
   </p>
